{
  "cast": "/assets/tutorials/tutorial-forking.cast",
  "language": "et",
  "version": 1,
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.422355,
      "replayEndSec": 12.478171,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-01.2f627b22.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.15102,
      "textHash": "2f627b22641ccde22e2d5e1dae446ff47645af491bf680782ac69cb5664c9769",
      "narrationText": "Teeme repositooriumist forki ühe käsuga. See kloonib kõik -- rakenduse, andmebaasi, konfiguratsioonifailid. Ja see juhtub sekunditega, olenemata repositooriumi suurusest. Üks gigabait, sada gigabaiti, üks terabait: sama aeg, iga kord.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-01-after.461471d1.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.552653,
      "afterTextHash": "461471d1cd02998a3243cb26510bd3aadb1da2f404f061cfc34cd7ae8c4adb9f"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 12.478171,
      "replayEndSec": 18.050071,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-02.f9334190.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 7.88898,
      "textHash": "f9334190b2f7c6803613df56763a9b4d48e742de07642c9936af00ce771f9402",
      "narrationText": "Mõlemad repositooriumid eksisteerivad nüüd kõrvuti. Sama masin, sama ketas, kaks täiesti sõltumatut keskkonda. Forkil on oma konteinerid, oma failisüsteem ja oma Dockeri deemon.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-02-after.0db6276f.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.866122,
      "afterTextHash": "0db6276f21b58e075539726da8a131f40cd65ddd59b36ca71fa440a23abb55ed"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 18.050071,
      "replayEndSec": 25.352583,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-03.7d9d0a3a.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.325714,
      "textHash": "7d9d0a3af2f797109c5c88630d5990c32e11faf8d070fdd5da58d2f252f40986",
      "narrationText": "Tõestame isolatsiooni. Originaalis on meie markerifail täpselt seal, kuhu me selle jätsime. Forki olemasolu ei ole originaalis midagi muutnud.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-03-after.6a012f89.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.474286,
      "afterTextHash": "6a012f895035005a7cf85510aab5258cd094c54b83e73e9fcc7d9e26742bd8e8"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 25.352583,
      "replayEndSec": 33.706234,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-04.ce85c437.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 5.877551,
      "textHash": "ce85c4377c7c17a778906d10e858cfbaca6d2cbd7b798ef04774466821803c6a",
      "narrationText": "Nüüd kustutame selle faili -- kuid ainult forki sees. Forki sees on see kadunud. Tegime hävitava muudatuse ja see jäi forki sisse.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-04-after.846d677e.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.082449,
      "afterTextHash": "846d677eb0b4cbc764d2ee591d378d0003d09ebbb377805f042ebe172de921ce"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 33.706234,
      "replayEndSec": 41.0794,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-05.a0d89b45.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.437551,
      "textHash": "a0d89b45c839af6f9f38d65d32b8422f026ae32f101c36440c68833f2d70c88e",
      "narrationText": "Tagasi originaalile. Markerifail on siin ikka alles, puutumata. Originaal ei teadnud, et midagi juhtus. Samad kujutised, eraldi Dockeri deemonid, eraldi failisüsteemid.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-05-after.5255fd6a.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.847347,
      "afterTextHash": "5255fd6a0838c1079ccd5f13bf3757ac9f9a0f5151dec8f629ad7a75a3d5f0da"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-06",
      "markerIndex": 5,
      "replayStartSec": 41.0794,
      "replayEndSec": 48.135359,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-06.3480d69d.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.03102,
      "textHash": "3480d69d3d1c4105f8d065f38bc5111dbb1751b005842a06eb0e63b3ffcc0fb0",
      "narrationText": "Kui oled lõpetanud, kustuta lihtsalt fork. Originaal jääb täpselt selliseks, nagu ta oli. Tee fork, katse, riku asju, kustuta -- riskita.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-06-after.dc610654.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.709388,
      "afterTextHash": "dc6106548e42c093c327d461690d3f67a23aa41574af8d2e51512854a2ba39cf"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/intro.52c78504.mp3",
      "textHash": "52c78504c16cab19064aa718534c5c7ea5a90ed6ad63a1b91aa79e13a4eb34e8",
      "audioDurationSec": 6.844082,
      "narrationText": "Tere tulemast tapja-funktsiooni juurde! Klooni terve tootmisrepo sõltumata suurusest ja ära riku midagi."
    },
    {
      "id": "fan-out",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/fan-out.d6195195.mp3",
      "textHash": "d61951959b64025bc25317d24dc0448393cc8efc4a1d599a13b53f5c5bfacebb",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.874286,
      "narrationText": "Üks vanemrepo hargneb nii paljudeks sõltumatuteks kloonideks, kui soovid. Iga fork on oma isoleeritud keskkond, mis töötab originaaliga kõrvuti."
    },
    {
      "id": "link-speed",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/link-speed.1418de94.mp3",
      "textHash": "1418de940e96edd8372967a1aaff5f0ce75947d33f9b7b7611cf44e892b67690",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.907755,
      "narrationText": "Mõtle, nagu jagaksid kausta linki. Link on sama kerge asi, olgu kaust väike või tohutu, ja forkimine töötab sama põhimõtte alusel."
    },
    {
      "id": "scale-invariance",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/scale-invariance.7dda1e54.mp3",
      "textHash": "7dda1e54aa5f757dafc83745b07dbfa7894e383f9213777fa5531f7a3f539a1c",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.527347,
      "narrationText": "Üks gigabait, sada gigabaiti, üks terabait: fork käitub samamoodi. Repo suurus ei tule võrrandisse."
    },
    {
      "id": "sun-mirrors",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/sun-mirrors.1207afb5.mp3",
      "textHash": "1207afb52238d7058dc8922459c141d46eea41044e6e6f8ff996b5af37d6ccbc",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.605714,
      "narrationText": "Vanemrepo on päike ja sinu fork on peegel, mis selle valgust püüab. Jagatud alus jääb puutumata, samas kui kõik, mida sa peeglile maalid, kuulub ainult sulle."
    },
    {
      "id": "river-photo",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/river-photo.c385ec2d.mp3",
      "textHash": "c385ec2d7cf03016cc2ff92f09c2a14d0a6573674a7c260b2b73ec01287b18fa",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.639184,
      "narrationText": "Fork on vanema külmutatud foto ühel hetkel. Vanem voolab edasi nagu jõgi, kuid sinu hetkpilt jääb täpselt sinna, kus oli."
    },
    {
      "id": "flat-disk",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/flat-disk.959411f0.mp3",
      "textHash": "959411f0a3c033f1a2e90cc1a91b6c1341964cd79fd4d6236d5988441253019a",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.560816,
      "narrationText": "Viis forki saja gigabaidisest repost moodustavad kettal ikkagi umbes sada gigabaiti. Sa maksad ainult baitide eest, mida tegelikult iga forki sees muudad."
    },
    {
      "id": "next-tutorial",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-forking/next-tutorial.1c0080c0.mp3",
      "textHash": "1c0080c0639e9ce66487d9c4cca3a7cd3b163654743706a9672a212652f4127d",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.277551,
      "narrationText": "Sa nägid just käske. Nüüd muudame selle nähtavaks: päris andmebaasirakendus, fork'itud reaalajas, kõrvuti muudetud, ja originaal ei võpata kordagi."
    }
  ],
